In214C*                  MOVEL(P)  T0CUST        @EMCODE                                            
In214C*                  MOVEL(P)  T0NPCO        @EMNDOC                                            
In214C*                  MOVE      T0DATP        @EMFDOC                                            
In214C*                  MOVE      T0LINE        @EMLDOC                                            
In214C                   MOVEL(P)  T0CIA1        @EMCIAA                                            
In214C                   MOVEL(P)  T0DLG1        @EMDLGA                                            
In214C                   MOVEL(P)  T0PRVR        @EMCODE                                            
In214C                   MOVEL(P)  T0NPC1        @EMNDOC                                            
In214C                   MOVE      T0DAT1        @EMFDOC                                            
In214C                   MOVE      T0LIN1        @EMLDOC                                            
      *                                                                                             
     C                   ENDSR                                                                      
