     C                   EVAL      T0TPE1=@PTPED                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0DAT1=@PDATP                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0NOP1=@PNOPL                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0LIN1=@PLINE                                                    
     C                                                                                              
