     C                   EVAL      T0DLGA=@PDLGA                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0NPCO=@PNPCO                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0TPED=@PTPED                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0DATP=@PDATP                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0NOPL=@PNOPL                                                    
     C                   EVAL      T0LINE=@PLINE                                                    
     C                                                                                              
